org.resthub.identity.model

Class AbstractPermissionsOwner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.resthub.identity.model.AbstractPermissionsOwner
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Group, User

    @Entity
public abstract class AbstractPermissionsOwner
extends Object

    Describe a generic class for users and groups. It contains/manage mainly permissions. When possible you SHOULD use method form the class and not from the permissions list

    Must be an entity to be references by permissions_owner_permissions and permissions_owner_groups
